1
00:00:49,634 --> 00:00:52,314
RECENT CALL: JAE-HO

2
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:57,973
This number is turned off.
You'll be connected to voicemail after...

3
00:01:01,729 --> 00:01:04,855
- Hello--
- How dare you lie so shamelessly?

4
00:01:04,938 --> 00:01:07,887
If you call Jae-ho one more time,

5
00:01:07,970 --> 00:01:10,096
I'll hunt you down and teach you a lesson!

6
00:01:10,179 --> 00:01:11,319
Where are you right--

7
00:01:59,466 --> 00:02:00,765
Hey, Mom.

8
00:02:01,474 --> 00:02:03,560
Sorry I called you so late.

9
00:02:04,251 --> 00:02:07,780
I've been so busy
I didn't realize a week passed already.

10
00:02:11,643 --> 00:02:13,884
Mom, what's wrong?

11
00:02:13,967 --> 00:02:16,923
- Yu-mi.
- Mom, let me talk to Dad.

12
00:02:17,006 --> 00:02:18,860
Yu-mi, it's your neighbor.

13
00:02:18,943 --> 00:02:20,050
Hello. Can you--

14
00:02:20,133 --> 00:02:21,741
Don't be startled.

15
00:02:21,824 --> 00:02:25,364
Your father passed away.

16
00:02:25,447 --> 00:02:27,693
He lost consciousness two days ago,

17
00:02:27,776 --> 00:02:29,730
and he passed away this morning.

18
00:02:31,095 --> 00:02:33,245
What are you talking about?

19
00:02:34,456 --> 00:02:35,898
Can you come?

20
00:03:36,701 --> 00:03:37,791
Yu-mi.

21
00:03:49,754 --> 00:03:51,023
He had cancer.

22
00:03:53,149 --> 00:03:55,685
They were going to tell you
before you left,

23
00:03:57,267 --> 00:03:59,053
but your father wouldn't allow it.

24
00:04:00,899 --> 00:04:02,678
He didn't want to get in your way.

25
00:04:14,902 --> 00:04:16,015
Yu-mi...

26
00:04:35,002 --> 00:04:40,039
LATE LEE SANG-HO

27
00:04:52,323 --> 00:04:53,369
I'll

28
00:04:56,374 --> 00:04:58,718
just try my hardest now.

29
00:05:03,077 --> 00:05:05,071
I'm sorry for everything.

30
00:05:12,365 --> 00:05:13,663
Hey, Yu-mi.

31
00:05:15,283 --> 00:05:16,953
Hi, Jae-ho.

32
00:05:18,501 --> 00:05:20,230
Why do you live your life like that?

33
00:05:23,645 --> 00:05:26,008
Shouldn't you at least make an excuse?

34
00:05:29,076 --> 00:05:30,391
I was

35
00:05:33,302 --> 00:05:35,553
planning to tell you first,

36
00:05:39,715 --> 00:05:41,597
but it was too hard.

37
00:05:45,251 --> 00:05:46,510
You're crazy.

38
00:06:07,163 --> 00:06:09,615
Hello, Sir. This is Yu-mi.

39
00:06:11,331 --> 00:06:12,966
Yes, Yu-mi from Baekma.

40
00:06:15,605 --> 00:06:17,751
Is it possible to sell our shop?

41
00:06:21,052 --> 00:06:22,863
Even if it's for cheap?

42
00:06:27,908 --> 00:06:29,247
Okay, I understand.

43
00:06:37,261 --> 00:06:38,838
YU-MI, 300,000 WON

44
00:06:38,921 --> 00:06:41,358
YU-MI, 1.2 MILLION WON

45
00:06:45,234 --> 00:06:47,143
YU-MI, 1 MILLION WON

46
00:06:47,226 --> 00:06:49,452
YU-MI, 7.3 MILLION WON

47
00:06:57,632 --> 00:06:58,779
Who are you?

48
00:06:59,368 --> 00:07:01,370
I heard the owner here passed away.

49
00:07:02,423 --> 00:07:04,699
Yes. Why do you ask?

50
00:07:05,551 --> 00:07:09,868
He borrowed money from me last month.

51
00:07:11,384 --> 00:07:14,747
Now, who do I get that money back from?

52
00:07:22,673 --> 00:07:26,741
Please call me if anyone
shows interest in buying the shop.

53
00:07:26,824 --> 00:07:28,981
I'll send mom's living expenses monthly.

54
00:07:29,064 --> 00:07:30,502
Don't worry about her.

55
00:07:30,585 --> 00:07:32,428
It's better she stays with me.

56
00:07:32,511 --> 00:07:34,410
Focus on your job.

57
00:07:36,419 --> 00:07:40,335
Don't worry.
Call me and visit me often.

58
00:07:42,935 --> 00:07:43,938
I'll get going.

59
00:07:44,999 --> 00:07:46,197
Bye, Mom.

60
00:08:04,748 --> 00:08:07,044
I'm sorry.

61
00:08:08,518 --> 00:08:10,719
Take care.

62
00:08:25,347 --> 00:08:27,541
If you want to become
a ninth-grade civil servant in Seoul,

63
00:08:27,624 --> 00:08:30,173
it's mandatory to take Korean,
English, and Korean history.

64
00:08:30,256 --> 00:08:32,384
You have to take two electives too.

65
00:08:32,467 --> 00:08:35,005
The comprehensive course
is 450,000 won per month.

66
00:08:35,088 --> 00:08:37,666
BALANCE: 1,510,400 WON

67
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,911
Okay, I'll call back later.

68
00:08:47,537 --> 00:08:49,118
Four hundred and fifty thousand won...

69
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:51,663
BALANCE: 1,510,400 WON

70
00:08:56,493 --> 00:08:58,044
SMALL ROOM:
NO DEPOSIT, 350,000 WON A MONTH

71
00:08:58,127 --> 00:08:59,605
Three hundred and fifty thousand won.

72
00:09:09,223 --> 00:09:12,205
HIRING KITCHEN STAFF

73
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:21,806
That's 2,000 won.

74
00:09:21,889 --> 00:09:23,509
Happy birthday!

75
00:09:26,444 --> 00:09:27,619
PART-TIME JOBS

76
00:09:33,443 --> 00:09:34,429
Thank you.

77
00:09:56,802 --> 00:09:58,357
OFFICE JOB: COLLEGE OR UNIVERSITY DEGREE

78
00:10:07,768 --> 00:10:08,764
Yu-mi!

79
00:10:08,847 --> 00:10:09,913
Coming.

80
00:10:33,059 --> 00:10:36,004
MINIMUM REQUIREMENT:
COLLEGE OR UNIVERSITY DEGREE

81
